ing: 1 (10 ounce) box frozen chopped spinach, thawed and squeezed dry
1 (14 ounce) can artichoke hearts, chopped with hard leaf tips removed
1 (1 ounce) package dry ranch salad dressing mix
des: "If you like hot spinach artichoke dip, this is for you.  It's yummy and quick. Serve with crackers or garlic toast."
ins: In a large bowl, combine the cream cheese, spinach, feta cheese, artichokes, garlic and Ranch dressing mix. Mix together with clean hands until well blended. Form into a ball or log and set on a serving plate. Done!
